{"tid":783601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個平胸女朋友，真係慘過食屎！","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T09:19:49.000Z","uid":152262,"like":119,"dislike":413,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"1309ffd6b3c54e5a01c953a584ddd56f2f27dbff","tid":783601,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"溝佢果陣係上年冬天，著衫著得咁厚我只係望到佢個樣同對黑絲腳，結果中左大伏，去到情到濃時摸上去，咦，點解除左兩粒提子乾之外，好似咩都摸唔到咁，我屎忽兩舊肉仲好揸過佢！<br />\n<br />\n最大既問題就係佢又冇做錯D咩，其他野，樣腿性格都係100分，只係冇波姐，我又唔可以因為咁小事而飛佢，但諗諗下又唔覺得係小事，冇波就好似啲薯條冇落鹽，牛肉冇醃過，撈麵冇汁撈一樣，係殘缺，係食之無味，棄之可惜，而家個個禮拜俾佢chur黎啪啪啪，真係慘過食屎！"},{"pid":"2d337db05210266b2a55b2ba99ab055bfcd26218","tid":783601,"uid":69221,"like":72,"dislike":5,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"冇波真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6411ea662536f29cf0f7dacdf811e0052fb1f88d","tid":783601,"uid":52984,"like":136,"dislike":11,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"有女已經心滿意足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3cb497a236ec1fdbb1c2ffe2199ea635ce507c","tid":783601,"uid":100904,"like":9,"dislike":95,"score":-86,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"渣得多就大，以前我都冇波，而家都叫有C<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58528a726826cfba46f3dc84730b781e411f16b3","tid":783601,"uid":44416,"like":79,"dislike":4,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"咁你食屎啦，條女交俾我"},{"pid":"53795e5af698e184ad9bc2aa2c27d47fd081c002","tid":783601,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6411ea662536f29cf0f7dacdf811e0052fb1f88d","tid":783601,"uid":52984,"like":136,"dislike":11,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"有女已經心滿意足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}